Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:03.15,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}All my effort will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:06.30,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Endless desire,like a haunting refrairn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:09.56,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Such a pain ,the ideal versus the real
