Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须跟神大人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是乎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}准备中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}本店的开店时间为13:00
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}「Soft house柯莉～」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然13点才开门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间豆腐店早都开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是豆腐店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有八个小时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 现实太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那家店去打发时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是卖游戏的店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是这一带最大的店了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:32.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}一定能找到想要的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:32.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}复古游戏展销会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复古游戏展销会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展销会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大的店果然与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:43.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}店长推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:43.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}玩家领域3
